org.supercsv.cellprocessor.time

Class ParseLocalTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.supercsv.cellprocessor.CellProcessorAdaptor
      • org.supercsv.cellprocessor.time.AbstractTemporalAccessorParsingProcessor<LocalTime>
        • org.supercsv.cellprocessor.time.ParseLocalTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CellProcessor, StringCellProcessor

    public class ParseLocalTime
extends AbstractTemporalAccessorParsingProcessor<LocalTime>
    Converts a String to a LocalTime. For constructors using DateTimeFormatter, refer to the following classes:
    • DateTimeFormatter - formats by pattern and style
    • DateTimeFormatter - ISO 8601 formats
    • DateTimeFormatterBuilder - complex formats created via method calls
    Since:
    2.4.0
    Author:
    Ludovico Fischer
